    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Windsor armchairs with a horizontal U-shaped arm rail and back of medium height consisting of spindles contained within a curved bow anchored in the arm rail.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000014271/Evans, American Windsor Furniture (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sillones Windsor con una baranda de brazo horizontal en forma de U y respaldo de mediana altura consistente en husillos comprendidos dentro de un arco curvado afirmado en la baranda del brazo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
